<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦]</span> <span class="c4">[بَابٌ]</span> رَجُلٌ أَوْقَفَ عَلَى مَمَالِيكَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٥٤-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا الْمَرْوَزِيُّ أَنَّهُ قَالَ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَأَيْشِ تَقُولُ إِنْ هُوَ قَالَ إِنَّ ضَيْعَتِي وَقْفٌ عَلَى مَمَالِيكِي؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> عَلَى الْمَمَالِيكِ لَا يَسْتَقِيمُ يُوقِفُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَيَعْتِقُهُمْ؟<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> جَائُزٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَإِنْ مَاتَ الْعَبِيدُ وَلَهُمْ أَوْلَادٌ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لَهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> وَإِنْ كَانَ لَهُمْ بَنَاتٌ؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ وَقَالَ: إِنْ مَاتَ الْمَمَالِيكُ وَلَيْسَ لَهُمْ وَلَدٌ رَجَعَتِ الضَّيْعَةُ إِلَى الْعُصْبَةِ. فَإِنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ عُصْبَةٌ بِيعَتِ الضَّيْعَةُ وَفُرِّقَتْ عَلَى الْمَسَاكِينِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>